"mengelola) file AppImage di desktop Linux Anda. Jika Anda menggunakan distro "
"berbasis Debian (Ubuntu, Mint, dll...), ada PPA resmi AppImageLauncher:"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:117
msgid "Linux (PPA)"
msgstr "Linux (PPA)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:119
msgid ""
"For Debian-based Linux distributions (Ubuntu, Mint, etc...), we also have a "
"PPA (Personal Package Archive), which adds our official OpenShot software "
"repository to your package manager, making it possible to install our latest "
"version, without relying on our AppImages."
msgstr ""
"Untuk distribusi Linux berbasis Debian (Ubuntu, Mint, dll...), kami juga "
"memiliki PPA (Personal Package Archive), yang menambahkan repositori "
"perangkat lunak resmi OpenShot ke manajer paket Anda, sehingga memungkinkan "
"untuk menginstal versi terbaru kami tanpa bergantung pada AppImage kami."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:124
msgid "Stable PPA (Contains only official releases)"
msgstr "PPA Stabil (Hanya berisi rilis resmi)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:133
msgid "Daily PPA (Highly experimental and unstable, for testers)"
msgstr "PPA Harian (Sangat eksperimental dan tidak stabil, untuk penguji)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:142
msgid "Chrome OS (Chromebook)"
msgstr "Chrome OS (Chromebook)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:144
msgid ""
"Chrome OS supports Linux apps, but this feature is off by default. You can "
"turn it on in *Settings*. Once Linux is enabled, you can install and run "
"OpenShot Linux AppImages on any *x86-based* Chromebook. The command below "
"will download our AppImage and configure your system to run OpenShot "
"successfully."
msgstr ""
"Chrome OS mendukung aplikasi Linux, tetapi fitur ini mati secara default. "
"Anda dapat mengaktifkannya di *Pengaturan*. Setelah Linux diaktifkan, Anda "
"dapat menginstal dan menjalankan OpenShot Linux AppImage di Chromebook "
"berbasis *x86* mana pun. Perintah di bawah ini akan mengunduh AppImage kami "
"dan mengonfigurasi sistem Anda untuk menjalankan OpenShot dengan sukses."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:149
msgid "Navigate to *chrome://os-settings/crostini* (Copy/Paste)"
msgstr "Buka *chrome://os-settings/crostini* (Salin/Tempel)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:150
msgid "Under \"Linux (Beta)\" select \"Turn On\". Default values are fine."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah \"Linux (Beta)\" pilih \"Nyalakan\". Nilai default sudah cukup."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:152
msgid ""
"When the Terminal appears (i.e. black window), Copy/Paste the following "
"command:"
msgstr ""
"Saat Terminal muncul (misalnya jendela hitam), Salin/Tempel perintah berikut:"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:152
msgid ""
"``bash <(wget -O - http://openshot.org/files/chromeos/install-stable.sh)``"
msgstr ""
"``bash <(wget -O - http://openshot.org/files/chromeos/install-stable.sh)``"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:155
msgid "Previous Versions"
msgstr "Versi Sebelumnya"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:157
msgid ""
"To download old versions of OpenShot Video Editor, you can visit https://"
"github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tags. Click on the version number you need, "
"and scroll to the bottom, under the release notes. You will find download "
"links for each operating system. Download the appropriate version for your "
"computer, and follow the installation instructions above."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengunduh versi lama OpenShot Video Editor, Anda dapat mengunjungi "
"https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tags. Klik nomor versi yang Anda "
"butuhkan, dan gulir ke bawah, di bawah catatan rilis. Anda akan menemukan "
"tautan unduhan untuk setiap sistem operasi. Unduh versi yang sesuai untuk "
"komputer Anda, dan ikuti petunjuk instalasi di atas."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:162
msgid ""
"NOTE: Projects (\\*.osp) made with newer versions of OpenShot Video Editor "
"might not support older versions."
msgstr ""
"CATATAN: Proyek (\\*.osp) yang dibuat dengan versi OpenShot Video Editor "
"yang lebih baru mungkin tidak didukung oleh versi yang lebih lama."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:165
msgid "Uninstall"
msgstr "Copot pemasangan"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:167
msgid ""
"To fully uninstall OpenShot from your system, you must **manually delete** "
"the ``.openshot_qt`` folder: ``~/.openshot_qt/`` or ``C:\\Users\\USERNAME\\."
"openshot_qt\\``, which contains all settings and files used by OpenShot. Be "
"sure to **backup** any recovery files of your existing projects first (\\*."
"osp files). Please see :ref:`preferences_reset_ref` for instructions on "
"clearing the previous ``openshot.settings`` file (for a clean install with "
"**default preferences**)."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghapus OpenShot sepenuhnya dari sistem Anda, Anda harus **menghapus "
"secara manual** folder ``.openshot_qt``: ``~/.openshot_qt/`` atau ``C:"
"\\Users\\USERNAME\\.openshot_qt\\``, yang berisi semua pengaturan dan file "
"yang digunakan oleh OpenShot. Pastikan untuk **mencadangkan** file pemulihan "
"dari proyek Anda yang ada terlebih dahulu (file \\*.osp). Silakan lihat :ref:"
"`preferences_reset_ref` untuk petunjuk menghapus file ``openshot.settings`` "
"sebelumnya (untuk instalasi bersih dengan **preferensi default**)."

